title: Executive Order 7921-Extending the Existence of the Quetico-Superior Committee, Created by Executive Order No. 6783 of June 30, 1934
content: By virtue of the authority vested in me as President of the United States, I hereby extend the existence of the Quetico-Superior Committee, created by Executive Order No. 6783 of June 30, 1934, for a period of four years, from June 30, 1938 to June 30, 1942.
citation: Franklin D. Roosevelt, Executive Order 7921-Extending the Existence of the Quetico-Superior Committee, Created by Executive Order No. 6783 of June 30, 1934 Online by Gerhard Peters and John T. Woolley, The American Presidency Project https://www.presidency.ucsb.edu/node/368773
